metadata.name: angelic soul in a devilish body
metadata.description:
Having ended up in hell 
and disappointed in the whole world, 
walling up her feelings in a box 
so as not to feel more pain, 
she continues on her way. 
Having built a protective wall 
around herself 
and not letting anyone near her, 
armed to the teeth
she lived in resentment against God 
for sending her to hell. 
Unaware
that the most powerful weapon 
is the inner light, 
which will lead her out of her own darkness,
where will she find heaven on earth.



size 4000x5000
